- Oh.

01:14.950 --> 01:16.360
Just be careful with the cigar.

01:16.451 --> 01:19.238
Used to be a man drove the car.
Now the car drives the man.

01:19.329 --> 01:20.489
Go on. Turn it over.

01:21.540 --> 01:25.203
- Here? Is it, uh...
- Go on. It's in neutral.

