01:43.604 --> 01:45.515
If my wife knew I was here,
she'd kill me.

01:45.606 --> 01:47.016
What a way to go.

01:47.107 --> 01:49.849
- Yeah.
- I see you're admiring the seats.

01:49.860 --> 01:53.694
That's pigskin and calfskin.

01:53.780 --> 01:55.111
Hand rubbed.

01:55.198 --> 01:57.905
Nicest piece of furniture I own
would be in the garage.

01:57.909 --> 01:59.615
Try the radio.

01:59.703 --> 02:03.070
The only thing that sounds
better than the engine is the radio.

02:07.669 --> 02:10.752
<i>The Russians have beaten</i>
<i>us into outer space.</i>

02:10.756 --> 02:13.463
<i>You are listening</i>
<i>to the sound of</i> Sputnik,

02:13.550 --> 02:16.417
<i>a satellite launched</i>
<i>this morning via rocket,</i>

02:16.511 --> 02:19.253
<i>in orbit, right now,</i>
<i>directly over our heads.</i>

02:19.264 --> 02:24.224
<i>A sound that says</i>
<i>all is not well with America.</i>

02:24.686 --> 02:26.768
America doesn't own the 300.

02:32.527 --> 02:34.688
<i>Oh, the shark, babe</i>

02:35.405 --> 02:38.021
<i>Has such teeth, dear</i>

02:38.575 --> 02:41.157
<i>And he shows them</i>

02:41.244 --> 02:43.951
<i>Pearly white</i>

02:43.955 --> 02:46.788
<i>Just a jackknife</i>

02:46.792 --> 02:50.000
<i>Has old Macheath, babe</i>

02:50.087 --> 02:55.127
<i>And he keeps it out of sight</i>

02:55.133 --> 02:56.919
<i>You know when that shark bites</i>

02:58.387 --> 03:01.254
<i>With his teeth, babe</i>

03:01.348 --> 03:03.054
<i>Scarlet billows</i>

03:03.975 --> 03:06.933
<i>Start to spread</i>

03:06.937 --> 03:09.428
<i>Fancy gloves, oh</i>

03:09.439 --> 03:12.602
<i>Wears old Macheath, babe</i>

03:12.609 --> 03:14.770
<i>So there's never</i>

03:14.861 --> 03:17.147
<i>Never a trace of red</i>

03:18.490 --> 03:21.106
<i>Now on the sidewalk</i>
<i>Uh-huh, uh-huh</i>

03:21.118 --> 03:24.281
<i>Ooh, Sunday mornin', uh-huh</i>

03:24.287 --> 03:26.869
<i>Lies a body</i>

03:26.957 --> 03:28.117
<i>Just oozin' life</i>

03:29.793 --> 03:33.001
<i>And someone's sneakin'</i>

03:33.004 --> 03:35.962
<i>'Round the corner</i>

03:35.966 --> 03:38.503
<i>Could that someone</i>

03:38.510 --> 03:40.466
<i>Be Mack the Knife?</i>

03:41.471 --> 03:44.338
<i>Now did ya hear about Louie Miller</i>

03:44.349 --> 03:47.637
<i>He disappeared, babe</i>

03:47.644 --> 03:49.805
<i>After drawin' out</i>

03:50.313 --> 03:52.975
<i>All his hard-earned cash</i>

03:53.066 --> 03:56.024
<i>And now Macheath spends</i>

03:56.027 --> 03:59.019
<i>Just like a sailor</i>

03:59.656 --> 04:04.992
<i>Could it be our boy's done</i>
<i>somethin' rash?</i>

04:05.078 --> 04:06.659
<i>Ah, Jenny Diver</i>

04:07.789 --> 04:11.031
<i>Hey, Suki Tawdry</i>

04:11.126 --> 04:13.868
<i>Ooh, Miss Lotte Lenya</i>

04:13.879 --> 04:17.166
<i>And old Lucy Brown</i>

04:17.173 --> 04:19.711
<i>Oh, the line forms</i>

